summary: Olga is a Managing Partner and co-founder at Spartexa. She has been leading the company towards its goals in supporting and accomplishing the transformation of the oil and gas industry into an AI-fueled business. She has extensive engineering experience in various upstream projects across the globe while working for international exploration, operational and consulting companies. Olga holds an Executive MSc in Business Administration from Rotterdam School of Management Erasmus University. Her entrepreneurial spirit and hands-on insights into the needs of the upstream domain drive her to create value for positive change.
